name: Onslow County Health Department
tweet: Mammograms can help find breast cancer early, before it spreads.  If you are age 40 to 49, talk with your doctor about when to start getting mammograms and how often to get them. If you are age 50 to 74, get mammograms every 2 years. You may also choose to get them more often.  https://t.co/X72RYjhDB9
